# PERSONAL ESCROW SAVINGS APP — FRONTEND COPY
# File: frontend/text.tx
# Purpose: UI copy + labels + microcopy for a personal escrow-based savings layer
# Tone: Clear, calm, trustworthy, practical
# Notes: Avoid legal advice. Keep statements plain-language.

[APP_NAME]
EscrowSave

[TAGLINE]
Save with guardrails.

[ONE_LINER]
A personal escrow layer that locks your savings until you choose to release it — on your terms.

