[SECTION:PROBLEM]
headline=Saving is easy. Not touching it is the hard part.
body=We built a personal escrow layer that adds friction where it matters, without blocking you from emergencies.
points=Locks savings by default | You decide release rules | Clear, predictable fees

[SECTION:HOW_IT_WORKS]
headline=How the escrow savings layer works
step1_title=Create a goal
step1_body=Name your goal, set a target, and choose how you want releases handled.
step2_title=Deposit into escrow
step2_body=Move money into your vault. It’s held and tracked separately from spendable funds.
step3_title=Release when ready
step3_body=Unlock on schedule or by request. You stay in control.

[SECTION:FEATURES]
headline=Designed to keep savings intact
f1_title=Escrow vault
