[FAQ]
q1=What is a personal escrow vault?
a1=It’s a dedicated savings layer that holds your funds until you choose to release them.
q2=Can I access my money anytime?
a2=Yes. You can request a standard release or use emergency unlock if needed.
q3=Is my money insured?
a3=We partner with regulated financial institutions for custody and protections.
q4=What if I change my mind?
a4=You can adjust or pause your release rules at any time.

